<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id8ebcc242-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s284dd"><num value="284dd">§ 284dd.</num><heading> Twentieth replenishment</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id8ebcc243-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s284dd/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> In general</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The United States Governor of the International Development Association is authorized to contribute on behalf of the United States $3,500,000,000 to the twentieth replenishment of the resources of the Association, subject to obtaining the necessary appropriations.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id8ebcc244-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s284dd/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In order to pay for the United States contribution provided for in subsection (a), there are authorized to be appropriated, without fiscal year limitation, $3,500,000,000 for payment by the Secretary of the Treasury.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="id8ebcc245-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/pl/86/565/s32">Pub. L. 86–565, § 32</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/pl/117/328/dK/tVII/s7072/a">Pub. L. 117–328, div. K, title VII, § 7072(a)</ref>, <date date="2022-12-29">Dec. 29, 2022</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/136/5091">136 Stat. 5091</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
